data.description:
THIS IS THE ONE*** GREAT INVESTMENT*** GATED COMMUNITY NEAR 30A***BUILT IN 2021** Discover the epitome of luxurious living in the coveted Lakeview Estates, a serene, gated community nestled just 1.36 miles from the beaches of 30A. This magnificent property, priced under $900,000 represents an exceptional opportunity in this highly desirable location.Lakeview Estates is known for its tranquility and exclusivity, featuring a beautiful community pool and a picturesque, stocked Pond. There are 46 homes in the community. Embrace the peace of a no short-term rental policy, ideal for a primary residence or a vacation home.The proximity to 30A means you're just a brief golf cart or bike ride away from the pristine sandy shores and the vibrant atmosphere of 30A, famed for its unique shopping, dining experiences, and breathtaking South Walton beaches , walking and biking paths.
This home, showcasing the popular Victoria floor plan, offers a harmonious blend of elegance and comfort. The design features four spacious bedrooms and 2.5 baths, with a split-bedroom layout centered around an expansive open-concept living and dining area - perfect for both relaxation and entertainment. The 9-foot ceilings, granite countertops, shaker-style cabinetry, and EVP flooring throughout main living area. The tray ceilings with crown molding in various rooms, including the foyer, dining, family room, and master bedroom, add a touch of luxury.
The master suite, a tranquil retreat, includes a generous walk-in closet and a luxurious bath with dual sinks and a separate tiled shower. The kitchen is a chef's delight equipped with upgraded cabinets, granite countertops, a central island with an apron farm sink, a 5-burner gas stovetop, stainless steel appliances, and a sizeable walk-in pantry.  

In addition to its aesthetic appeal, this home is a true modern marvel, equipped with smart home technology. Enjoy high-speed internet with landlines in every room, smart locks on exterior doors, smart lighting, ADT security, a smart garage, and an irrigation system - all controllable via your smartphone. The screened-in back porch and beautifully landscaped yard with an irrigation system provide the perfect setting.   .
Don't miss your chance to own this spectacular home in Lakeview Estates. Contact me today to learn more about this extraordinary community and to schedule a viewing. Your dream home near 30A is waiting for you.  

This is a list of Updates and Upgrades
"	New fans in Rooms and living room
"	Fan on the back porch
"	Dining room, bathroom, and kitchen lighting 
"	Kitchen cabinet Hardware 
"	Custom Kitchen Backsplash 
"	Kitchen Faucet 
"	Upgraded dishwasher 
"	Blinds (Allen+Roth cordless blackout blinds throughout  
"	Back door with integrated privacy blinds 
"	Closed in the back patio 
"	Stone work landscaping 
"	Attic door with attic storage 
"	Bike storage railings in the garage 
"	Gutters added  
"	Fruit trees young dwarf pomegranate and fig tree 
"	ADT Security Paid through August 7, 2024
"	Smart Door Lock System added to Front Door, Back Door, Garage Door
